ActHeritage Railway Stations Protection Act
SubjectTransfer of ownership of Canadian Pacific Railway Company Station in Nelson, British Columbia
PrecisOrder authorizing the Canadian Pacific Railway Company to transfer ownership, by way of donation, of its railway station in Nelson, British Columbia, to the City of Nelson.
